---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
---

<MainLayout title="About | Jorge Obando">
  <section class="about-hero">
    <p class="eyebrow">About</p>
    <h1>Building systems that turn complexity into measurable impact.</h1>
    <p class="lead">
      Director of Product Design with 25+ years of experience leading enterprise platforms,
      AI integration, and global design organizations.
    </p>
    <p class="supporting">
      I operate at the intersection of strategy, systems, and execution—aligning product,
      engineering, data, and leadership to deliver scalable, outcome-driven experiences.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="about-main">
    <div class="about-copy about-copy-wide">
      <h2>Professional Narrative</h2>
      <p>
        As a Director of Product Design, I lead initiatives that transform complex business
        challenges into scalable, AI-enhanced platforms. My work focuses on aligning strategic
        intent with execution—ensuring that design decisions drive measurable outcomes.
      </p>
      <p>
        Over the course of my career, I have worked across enterprise environments and
        high-growth organizations, leading cross-functional teams and building systems that
        operate at scale.
      </p>
      <p>
        I integrate AI not as a feature, but as a lever for solving meaningful problems—through
        predictive systems, intelligent workflows, and decision frameworks that balance
        automation with human judgment.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <p class="section-label">Philosophy</p>
    <h2>What I Believe</h2>

    <div class="three-up-grid">
      <div class="card">
        <p>Strategic design decisions should drive measurable business outcomes.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <p>AI integration should solve real problems with transparency.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <p>Cross-functional alignment accelerates impact.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <p>Ethical and inclusive design builds trust at scale.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <p class="section-label">Core Strengths</p>
    <h2>What I Bring</h2>

    <div class="three-up-grid">
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Research &amp; Insight</h3>
        <p>Turning signals into actionable product direction.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h3>Systems Design</h3>
        <p>Building scalable platforms and workflows.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h3>AI Experience</h3>
        <p>Designing intelligent, data-driven systems.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h3>Leadership</h3>
        <p>Aligning teams and delivering at scale.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="personal">
    <p class="section-label">Beyond the Work</p>
    <h2>Perspective</h2>

    <div class="about-grid">
      <div>
        <p>
          I was born in Costa Rica and grew up across multiple countries. This global perspective
          shapes how I approach design—valuing context, balance, and diversity of thought.
        </p>
        <p>
          My path into design began unexpectedly and evolved into a career spanning the full
          spectrum of product design, from early web systems to AI-enhanced platforms.
        </p>
        <p>
          Today, I live in New Jersey with my family. Their perspective grounds my work and
          continues to shape how I think about impact and responsibility.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="about-image-wrap">
        <img src="/images/personal.jpg" alt="Jorge Obando with Ariana" class="about-image" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="closing">
    <h2>From Perspective to Practice</h2>
    <p>
      The work that follows reflects how these principles translate into real systems,
      platforms, and measurable outcomes.
    </p>
    <a class="button button-primary" href="/case-studies">View Case Studies</a>
  </section>

  <style>
    .about-hero {
      margin-top: 48px;
      max-width: 720px;
    }

    .about-main {
      margin-top: 56px;
    }

    .about-copy-wide {
      max-width: 760px;
    }

    .about-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr) minmax(0, 1fr);
      gap: 40px;
      align-items: start;
    }

    .about-image-wrap {
      width: 100%;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: flex-start;
    }

    .about-image {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 420px;
      height: 320px;
      object-fit: cover;
      object-position: center;
      border-radius: 16px;
      border: 1px solid #dddddd;
      display: block;
    }

    .three-up-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 16px;
    }

    .card {
      border: 1px solid #e5e5e5;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      background: #ffffff;
    }

    .personal {
      margin-top: 80px;
    }

    .closing {
      margin-top: 80px;
      max-width: 760px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 720px) {
      .about-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .three-up-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .about-image {
        max-width: 100%;
        height: 280px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</MainLayout>